00:03:28,123 --> 00:03:30,001
began mocking me.

90
00:03:30,001 --> 00:03:30,929
He was walking around saying,

91
00:03:30,929 --> 00:03:32,742
"Maybe, maybe, maybe."

92
00:03:32,742 --> 00:03:34,021
(Bob snickers)

93
00:03:34,021 --> 00:03:36,411
All right, I'm gonna make up
a little lavender color here,

