I'm just gonna tap the bristles into that.

101
00:03:53,796 --> 00:03:55,407
(brush tapping on palette)

102
00:03:55,407 --> 00:03:58,031
Just tap a little bit, like so.

103
00:03:58,032 --> 00:04:00,719
Let's go up in here and let's
make some nice little clouds

104
00:04:00,718 --> 00:04:04,549
