and have fun all day.

105
00:04:04,549 --> 00:04:07,677
Just sorta wind 'em up
and put 'em in there, see.

106
00:04:08,270 --> 00:04:09,352
There.

107
00:04:10,937 --> 00:04:12,115
Okay.

108
00:04:13,027 --> 00:04:15,395
Wherever you think they should be.

109
00:04:15,395 --> 00:04:17,485
(brush swishing on canvas)

110
00:04:17,485 --> 00:04:18,670
I'm gonna just have 'em
come right over here.

111
00:04:18,670 --> 00:04:20,312
This is gonna be a big cliff, I think.

112
00:04:20,312 --> 00:04:23,818
A big rocky thing lives right there.

113
00:04:25,319 --> 00:04:26,686
Just drop it in.

114
00:04:26,685 --> 00:04:29,906
All right, there we go.

115
00:04:29,906 --> 00:04:31,649
And by using these little twisting

116
00:04:31,649 --> 00:04:33,718
or circular patterns here, it creates

117
00:04:33,718 --> 00:04:35,776
a multitude of little
things happening up here.

118
00:04:35,776 --> 00:04:38,336
It's not just a flat ol' dead sky.

119
00:04:38,336 --> 00:04:40,399
Lot of nice things going on.

120
00:04:40,980 --> 00:04:42,254
There.

121
00:04:42,795 --> 00:04:43,951
Okay.

122
00:04:44,437 --> 00:04:46,294
Maybe we'll come right over in here.

123
00:04:46,293 --> 00:04:49,384
And I'm just gonna put clouds
all over the sky like this.

124
00:04:51,449 --> 00:04:53,283
Okay, there we are.

