00:04:57,346 --> 00:04:58,939
Just load a little more color.

127
00:05:00,387 --> 00:05:01,308
There.

128
00:05:02,242 --> 00:05:04,389
Maybe there's a little
protrusion right out here.

129
00:05:04,389 --> 00:05:06,292
Wherever you want 'em.

130
00:05:06,660 --> 00:05:07,475
There.

131
00:05:08,985 --> 00:05:10,500
I tell you what, while I'm doing this,

132
00:05:10,500 --> 00:05:12,238
because this is going
to take just a second.

133
00:05:12,238 --> 00:05:14,307
I wanna show you one
of my little characters

134
00:05:14,307 --> 00:05:15,576
that's living with me now.

135
00:05:15,576 --> 00:05:18,968
I have three little baby
squirrels that I'm raising

