00:05:18,968 --> 00:05:20,461
and they are they cutest little devils.

137
00:05:20,461 --> 00:05:23,245
We took a little video of 'em,

138
00:05:23,245 --> 00:05:25,730
and I wanna share that with
you while I'm doing this.

139
00:05:25,730 --> 00:05:27,139
And I won't do anything
I don't tell you about

140
00:05:27,139 --> 00:05:30,651
while that's coming on there.

141
00:05:30,651 --> 00:05:32,326
Now these are tiny little baby ones.

142
00:05:32,326 --> 00:05:34,926
They're just beginning
to get a little fur.

