148
00:05:55,425 --> 00:05:57,419
It's just like goin' to the
doctor and gettin' your shot

149
00:05:57,418 --> 00:05:59,669
when it's feeding time here.

150
00:05:59,670 --> 00:06:03,391
We fill'er up and normally though,

151
00:06:03,391 --> 00:06:04,916
when you see a syringe comin' at you,

152
00:06:04,916 --> 00:06:09,844
sorta scares you a little
bit, but in this case,

153
00:06:09,845 --> 00:06:14,845
when my little friends here
see a syringe coming at 'em,

154
00:06:15,050 --> 00:06:16,372
they get excited.

155
00:06:16,372 --> 00:06:18,908
This just makes their whole day.

156
00:06:18,908 --> 00:06:21,908
It's hard to get 'em
to eat, as you can see.

157
00:06:21,908 --> 00:06:23,764
(Bob laughing)

158
00:06:23,764 --> 00:06:26,463
I think they'll eat
about every 15 minutes,

159
00:06:26,463 --> 00:06:27,946
if you'd feed 'em.

160
00:06:27,946 --> 00:06:30,624
I have three of those little rascals now

161
00:06:30,624 --> 00:06:33,706
and they live with me,
and my mother and I,

162
00:06:33,706 --> 00:06:38,610
and Nancy, we all take care
of these little devils.

163
00:06:38,610 --> 00:06:40,437
They're gonna soon be big enough

164
00:06:40,437 --> 00:06:42,788
to turn loose and let 'em go.

165
00:06:43,178 --> 00:06:43,832
There.

166
00:06:43,833 --> 00:06:45,529
I'm just putting in a few
little clouds down here,

167
00:06:45,528 --> 00:06:48,848
while you was watching
the little squirrels.

168
00:06:48,848 --> 00:06:50,704
Still just using the corner of the brush

169
