00:07:06,033 --> 00:07:08,418
All we're looking for is a little stain.

175
00:07:09,351 --> 00:07:10,465
There.

176
00:07:11,122 --> 00:07:13,992
Sometimes you can just decide where

177
00:07:13,992 --> 00:07:16,157
