darker, a little lighter.

178
00:07:16,156 --> 00:07:19,015
Shoot, maybe there's
even a little projection

179
00:07:19,016 --> 00:07:20,160
that comes right out through there.

180
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,088
See, that easy.

181
00:07:21,088 --> 00:07:22,903
Just by tapping.

182
00:07:22,903 --> 00:07:24,913
You can make all those little things.

183
00:07:25,346 --> 00:07:26,364
Okay.

184
00:07:26,947 --> 00:07:30,637
Grabbing another clean brush.

185
