This is clean, has nothing on it.

186
00:07:32,216 --> 00:07:33,420
It's very dry.

187
00:07:33,420 --> 00:07:35,937
And with that, you can just
begin blending this now.

188
00:07:35,937 --> 00:07:39,766
To any degree of softness
or harshness that you want.

189
00:07:39,766 --> 00:07:41,151
Just blend it.

190
00:07:41,711 --> 00:07:44,111
Aren't those little squirrels cute?

191
00:07:44,112 --> 00:07:46,309
I really like those little devils.

192
00:07:46,309 --> 00:07:48,218
They're so much fun.

