00:22:48,608 --> 00:22:52,846
come right along in here, and once again,

521
00:22:52,846 --> 00:22:55,374
this is a nice way of outlining

522
00:22:55,374 --> 00:22:59,178
and forming your stones and rocks.

523
00:23:01,327 --> 00:23:02,454
There.

524
00:23:02,454 --> 00:23:05,198
(brush tapping canvas)

525
00:23:05,740 --> 00:23:08,376
I want this one to remain quite dark.

