00:23:08,376 --> 00:23:11,368
Quite dark, so it doesn't
distract too much.

527
00:23:13,740 --> 00:23:15,345
There we go.

528
00:23:15,345 --> 00:23:20,345
Now you can take a clean,
dry, two-inch brush

