00:23:47,253 --> 00:23:50,023
We'll have a little splash,
comin' round down through here.

539
00:23:50,023 --> 00:23:52,271
(makes soft splashing sound)

540
00:23:52,271 --> 00:23:55,313
Shoot, maybe there's even a
