555
00:24:37,607 --> 00:24:41,197
I like it, it just enhances my paintings.

556
00:24:41,198 --> 00:24:44,824
Little bit of the nice highlight color.

557
00:24:45,480 --> 00:24:48,733
Let's see here, we could
take the liner brush,

